data.description: This home has so much character & charm, right in the heart of Dayton on a corner lot.  This updated home offers ceramic wood look tile throughout the home. Open floor plan from Living Room w/ reset lighting and tray ceiling to the dining room & large kitchen. The kitchen offers an amazing large island with quarts countertop and updated lighting.  Updated bathroom with oversize shower. Updated low e-windows, updated HVAC. Outdoors offers a covered cooking area with granite countertops and a hand painted Texas flag on the side of the storage building. The storage building is perfect for your lawn equipment or outdoor projects. Double driveway offering ample parking while BBQing with family & friends. There are several mature pecans trees and a producing peach tree too.  Call and schedule a showing before this one is gone.
